      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为akros2项目画一个启动依赖图。核心是akros2_bringup，它应该拉起其他几个模块。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "akros2_bringup"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，akros2_bringup作为中心节点。那它依赖哪些模块？我目前看到有description、base、teleop，还有msgs对吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "akros2_bringup",
        "akros2_description",
