    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，这四个都是直接依赖。不过我在想是不是还要加一个setup节点？有些配置是在bringup之前做的。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "setup",
        "akros2_bringup"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "好的，我把setup也加进来。那结构就是：bringup连到description、base、teleop、msgs这四个，setup暂时作为独立节点？",
